high_descs: Turn around, walk to the left until you reach the counter with the coffee machine on it.
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee machine.
Walk to the fridge to the right of the counter.
Place the mug on the top shelf of the fridge, cool it, then take it out.
Face the cabinet to the right of the fridge.
Place the mug in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Walk 2 steps, turn left for 2 steps, turn right for 4 steps and turn left and walk to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the coffee cup from the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk 5 steps and turn left to face the refrigerator,
Open the refrigerator and put the coffee cup on the stop shelf to the right of the green item, wait a few seconds and open the refrigerator and take out the coffee cup and close the door.
Turn around and takes a step, take a right for 2 steps and take another right, walk one step.
Open the bottom cabinet door on the far right of the counter, put the coffee cup in the cabinet toward the front, and shut the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup in the bottom right cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a mug from the coffee maker
Move to the fridge to the right of you
Chill the mug in the fridge before removing it and closing the door
Move to the cabinet closet to the fridge
Place the cup inside the bottom right cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in the cabinet on the bottom closest to the fridge.
